author: Jamie Feldman
title: 13 Of The World's Most Delicious Sandwiches, In 2 Minutes
text:
13 Of The World's Most Delicious Sandwiches, In 2 Minutes Time to get those passports in order. Jamie Feldman Associate Style Editor, The Huffington Post Posted: 08/03/2015 04:47 PM EDT 
Whether open-faced, crustless, pressed or in a pocket, the possibilities are pretty much endless with sandwiches, any way you slice them. 
The peanut-butter-and-jelly-loving United States is not the only country with a soft spot for subs. Thanks to a new video by Food People Places , it turns out there's a whole world (literally) of sandwiches to try. Some are loaded up with French fries, others are covered in melted cheese, and pretty much all of them will inspire you to book a flight somewhere ASAP. 
Of course, if a transatlanic trip isn't in your near future, you can also find the recipes for all these yummy sandwiches on the Food People Places website. 
Kind of puts your lunch to shame, no? Check out the video above.
